# Project Memory And Graphify

Before code or architecture work in this repository:

1. Read `vault/INDEX.md`.
2. Read `vault/00-Progetto/Protocollo-Collaborazione.md`.
3. Read `vault/00-Progetto/Memoria-AI.md`.
4. Read `vault/03-Bug/backlog.md`.
5. Read `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` before broad search or architecture answers.

Use the project wrapper for Graphify:

```bash
npm run graph:update
npm run graph:query -- "question"
npm run graph:path -- "A" "B"
npm run graph:explain -- "node"
npm run graph:check
```

After editing code, run `npm run graph:update` and `npm run graph:check`.
